task.summary: Add initial commit containing IDB185 2nd activity.

Add tests for Person, Place and Review in Models, Repositories and Services. Total of 31 tests. Add Application Context for Testing Environment. Add new dependencies: spring-test, pojo-tester, dbunit and spring-test-dbunit. Fix bug in PersonService saving FullName with Username value. Fix JPA relationship of Review in Person and Place, thanks to @mineda.
